rows.label: tlk70000123_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Recently see green barrels
all over place...

rows.label: tlk70000123_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Really want to bash them
open and see what inside.

rows.label: tlk70000123_04_msg0003
rows.name:
But sometimes barrels explode with
big bang, so dream of becoming
Driver could come to abrupt end!

rows.label: tlk70000123_04_msg0004
rows.name:
That where Driver like you
with true power come in!

rows.label: tlk70000123_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe there someone out there who
need you to break green barrels
for them! Person like Dolala...
